{"tid":2096140,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"清爽刮下「整塊油頭皮」！整層拿下來看得我頭也癢癢的","createTime":"2020-07-06T02:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T05:40:53.000Z","uid":28114,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1f9fca8dd4ba1b2bb430eccdc0d60d17a1791a","tid":2096140,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"※提醒：本文圖片及影片可能造成不適，請斟酌觀賞※<br />\n<br />\n嘿，你喜歡看噁心中帶點舒爽的療癒影片嗎？不用說，你一定喜歡的。今天早上花枝才發了一篇《為什麼你愛看「擠空史詩級巨痘」》，告訴大家喜歡看這種東西，完全就是人類本能，更是進化的證明。現在，我們又有一個見證的機會啦！<br />\n<br />\n今天要貼的，既不是巨痘，也不是耳屎，不過也是毫不遜色。本日主角就是～～頭皮屑！<br />\n<br />\n不曉得酸酸們有沒有頭皮屑的困擾，它們是頭皮皮膚上過度剝落的細胞，常常是因為脂漏性皮膚炎造成。對於那些嚴重的人來說，有事沒事撿起一塊頭皮屑，真的是滿常見的事QQ。今天這篇影片，就是把超大型頭皮削清理得乾乾淨淨！<br />\n<br />\n▼用小鑷子挑起來<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pics.ettoday.net/images/3075/3075428.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpics.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3075%2F3075428.gif&h=e7623989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼然後就可以咻咻～拉出來！<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pics.ettoday.net/images/3075/3075427.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpics.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3075%2F3075427.gif&h=3e422b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可、可惡，為什麼明明是令人困擾的頭皮屑，畫面卻這麼療癒呢？！我們就來看影片，體驗最原汁原味的感動～。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MA2PP-kaAV4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMA2PP-kaAV4&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=bc1b0da0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MA2PP-kaAV4</a><br />\n<br />\n▼成果超豐碩A_A<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pics.ettoday.net/images/3075/3075434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpics.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3075%2F3075434.jpg&h=ce64b9cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/pics.ettoday.net/images/3075/3075435.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fpics.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3075%2F3075435.jpg&h=02ceb953&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看著這樣的畫面，也不知道為什麼，就是有一種自己的頭皮好像也跟著清爽了的感受......。不過話又說回來啦，如果頭皮屑困擾真的非常嚴重的話，雖然像影片這樣動手弄下來也不會怎樣，還是去看看皮膚科比較好啦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/33204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F33204&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=b6c65469\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/33204</a>"},{"pid":"73b827f660f096af8e632a6e656f9762742ba7a2","tid":2096140,"uid":312363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T02:58:22.000Z","msg":"爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e889e32179f9cff7a218eaf3a272c6ed7b513d","tid":2096140,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:15:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef48c9a5673aef2447986fd4c43b20c0e31a50c","tid":2096140,"uid":35891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:20:43.000Z","msg":"好多人鍾意睇呢d片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇過有人用隻 假既膠耳 用暗瘡針挑d粉頭黑刺出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e688b0d849b0ece0f6668363dbc866dc12ddeb14","tid":2096140,"uid":30084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T03:40:54.000Z","msg":"拍果條友 R到自已捐哂都要R<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a9a049cb8d4ea9a99fd3495763d66065b85cb8","tid":2096140,"uid":116390,"like":0,"disl